user.biography: Ales, lagers, stouts, & more brewed in Portland, Maine and at @bbbthreerivers. Portland taproom open daily 🍻 Kitchen open Thursday through Sunday 🍔🥗🌮

node.text: Lil recap of our @austinstreetbrewery collab release party at @thirstyportland 💛 Big thanks to all who came out. Make sure to head to Austin Street’s Fox St. location today for both versions on draft + mixed 4-packs of both in cans (from noon until sell out)!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 08, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
We’ve got two of our absolute bedrock beers available in cans today, twin pillars representing everything we work towards day in and day out! 
7 taps and plenty of new hitters on the menu (barbacoa tacos, @goransonfarm salad and the ribeye cheesesteak are all good places to start) will make for a lovely Sunday. Bar 11am, kitchen 12pm, both through 5.

node.text:
Our ribeye cheesesteak on @solocucinamarket semolina is back on special all weekend, because you love it, and we love you. This sandwich + a tall Precept…..not sure we need to elaborate much here 🤤 
Bar & can sales from 11, kitchen from 12. 
🥩🥖🍺

node.text: Our ramp stores are winding down for the season, so we’re ripping our pork, kimchi & ramp quesadilla one more time till sellout! Ramp butter….🤤🤤🤤

node.text: Beautiful Maine summer days pair perfectly with Lux — she’s back in cans today!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'now hiring: EMPLOYEE WELLNESS & CULTURE MANAGER email resume & cover letter to: jobs@bissellbrothers.com'.

node.text:
We are hiring an Employee Wellness & Culture Manager! Swipe ↩️ or head to bissellbrothers.com/jobs for more details. If interested, please email cover letters and resumes to jobs@bissellbrothers.com by Friday, August 13th. 

We are passionate about finding the ideal candidate for this role, and understand that a variety of backgrounds and employment experiences can make someone skilled at this position. We encourage any passionate candidate to please apply, and include a cover letter that explains why you are interested in this role and passionate about working for our brewery.

This position will be eligible for Bissell Brothers' competitive benefits package, matching 401k, and is a great opportunity to join a passionate team.

We are an Equal Opportunity Employer and candidates from all backgrounds are encouraged to apply. We value diverse experiences and perspectives, and are committed to diversity and inclusion.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'now hiring: EMPLOYEE WELLNESS & CULTURE MANAGER email resume & cover letter to: jobs@bissellbrothers.com'.

Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'JOB DESCRIPTION The Employee Wellness & Culture Manager carries similar responsibilities as Human Resources Manager, but this position holds additional emphasis company and interpersonal communication, and in company culture. This position is responsible for assisting in the planning, development, implementation and administration of most of the functions that come Ûw with employment, recruitment, employee relations, compensation and benefits, compliance, and organizational development. This position will help develop and drive creative initiatives, and will advise company management in policy and program matters. AB'.
Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS Knowledge, skills, & abilities: Bachelor's degree in business or Human Resource experience preferred related field preferred a company of 50+ employees Broad generalist background including coaching and counseling, performance management, employee involvement, teambuilding, as well compensation and benefits Thorough knowledge of HR principles and federal/local regulations Experience in implementing and administering performance management programs, including annual reviews Exceptional project and personnel management skills Excellent ability to multi-task and prioritize in fast-growth environment busy, Proficiency in Microsoft Word, Excel, and PowerPoint is essential Exhibit extraordinary discretion, flexibility, and willingness to work in team environment'.
Photo by Bissell Brothers in Bissell Brothers with @embrodak.

node.text: Another week of classics — then next week brings the return of Preserve & Protect, our DIPA benefitting Friends of @baxterpark 🌲⛰ *NOTE* We are sold out of The Substance Ale cans until tomorrow (Tuesday 8/3).

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Bissell Brothers on August 02, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Every last 4-pack of Substance got snatched up over the weekend, so our flagship IPA is only available on draft today. There'll be more Subby cans tomorrow – until then we've got Nothing Gold (fresh off the line this morning!) plus Baby Genius and Precept available to go. All that and more pouring in the taproom from 11-9 ☀️

node.text: @marcuskingband & @nathanielrateliff pre-show energy is through the roof! Precept & Carne Asada tacos with white mole sauce is how we’re getting down. Kitchen closes at 7, bar at 9. 🌮🍺
